ONEBRUSH is your companion for better oral health.
Dentinostic by ONEBRUSH ONEBRUSH: The personal trainer for your teeth This sign in procedure is only required during your first start. After that, our app will remember you! By purchasing the ONEBRUSH toothbrush, you will be allowed to connect it to the app and track your brushing behaviour. You can use this app to receive a remote diagnosis from our dentist.

Welcome Dear patient! Our dentists are always available for you. Simply follow the diagnostic question & answer dialogue. Treatment swiftly Within 24h you will receive a diagnosis and an easy to understand doctor’s letter including a prescription, if required. This treatment will cost you 25 E only. Your data? \nThey are 100% safe
We treat your data and photos with absolute care. Nobody, except your doctor, will get access to this information. Above this, our entire processes are GDPR compliant. Register free of charge! In order to establish a file for you, we need your email address and further administrational data. Also these data are handled GDPR compliant for sure. Oops...
